Former Vice President of Nigeria and 2019 Peoples Democratic Party presidential candidate, Atiku Abubakar has reacted after he presented himself for screening at the PDP secretariat in Abuja.

The Peoples Democratic Party is holding a screening for its presidential aspirants. The screening committee is led by former Senate President, David Mark.
Atiku Abubakar, who is one of the leading aspirants from the northern part of Nigeria stated on his verified Facebook page that not even today’s rain could dampen his spirit as he presents himself for screening.

Recall that the former Vice President met with the National Working Committee (NWC) of the party yesterday.
The recent post by Atiku Abubakar has generated a lot of reactions from his fans and numerous followers.


